  },
  "judge_context": [
    "Should verify all six citation_detail fields are populated: `who` (U.S. Census Bureau), `what` (1850 U.S. Federal Census, population schedule), `when_created` (1850), `when_accessed`, `where` (FamilySearch.org with the NARA microfilm details), `where_within` (Schuylkill County, dwelling and family numbers)",
    "Should apply the replication test: a researcher with only this citation should be able to find the exact record — dwelling 84, family 91 is the level of specificity needed"
  ],
  "test": {
    "id": "ut_citation_001",
    "skill": "citation",
    "type": "positive"
  }
}

